                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The 'Pension Scheme' is implemented by the Bihar Building & Other Construction Workers Welfare Board (BBOCWWB), Labour Resources Department, Government of Bihar. Under this scheme, registered construction workers who have completed a minimum of five years of membership and have attained the age of 60 are eligible for a pension of ₹1,000/- per month. This benefit is provided only if the worker has not received a pension under any other social security scheme."
