        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The worker should be engaged in building or construction work.\n   1. The worker should be registered with the Bihar Building &amp;amp; Other Construction Workers Welfare Board.\n   1. The worker should have maintained continuous membership with the Board for a minimum of five years.\n   1. The worker should be 60 years of age or older.\n   1. The worker should not be receiving pension benefits under any other social security scheme.\n\n",
